# =============================================================================
# Storage Directory
# =============================================================================
# This directory exists only for local development. In production, all state
# is externalized:
#   - Cache → Redis
#   - Sessions → Redis
#   - Queues → Redis
#   - Files → Object Storage (S3/R2)
#   - Logs → stderr (CloudWatch/Datadog)
#
# Laravel requires these directories to exist at boot time, even if they're
# never written to (when using external drivers).
# =============================================================================

*
!.gitignore
